SELECT NodeStatBase.*, NodeStat.NumberTradRoutes AS Trad,NodeStat.NumberSportRoutes AS Sport,NodeStat.NumberTopRopeRoutes AS TopRope,NodeStat.NumberBoulderProblems AS Boulder,NodeStat.NumberAlpineRoutes AS Alpine,NodeStat.NumberIceRoutes AS Ice,NodeStat.NumberViaFerrataRoutes AS ViaFerrata,NodeStat.NumberDeepWaterRoutes AS DWS,RouteStat.NumberTradRoutes AS RTrad,RouteStat.NumberSportRoutes AS RSport,RouteStat.NumberTopRopeRoutes AS RTopRope,RouteStat.NumberBoulderProblems AS RBoulder,RouteStat.NumberAlpineRoutes AS RAlpine,RouteStat.NumberIceRoutes AS RIce,RouteStat.NumberViaFerrataRoutes AS RViaFerrata,RouteStat.NumberDeepWaterRoutes AS RDWS,NodeStat.NumberAscents,RouteStat.NumberAscents AS RNumberAscents,NodeStat.NumberRoutes,RouteStat.NumberRoutes AS RNumberRoutes FROM ( 
        SELECT 
          Node.NID AS NID,
          Node.Parent,
          Node.Hide,
          Node.NodeType,
          CA.Type AS AreaType,
          CA.Locked,
          Url.Lookup AS Stub,
          Nm.Name,
          HeirL.GPSFence,
          HeirL.BBoxPt2Long,
          HeirL.BBoxPt1Long,
          HeirL.BBoxPt2Lat,
          HeirL.BBoxPt1Lat,
          HeirL.CascadedBBoxPt2Long,
          HeirL.CascadedBBoxPt1Long,
          HeirL.CascadedBBoxPt2Lat,
          HeirL.CascadedBBoxPt1Lat,
          HeirL.PointLong,
          HeirL.PointLat,
          HeirL.CenterLong,
          HeirL.CenterLat,
          HeirL.HasLocatedChild,
          GROUP_CONCAT(T.Label SEPARATOR ',') AS Aspect
        FROM (
          SELECT 
            DISTINCT TargetNode.ID AS NID,
            TargetNode.Type AS NodeType,
            TargetNode.Parent,
            GREATEST(TargetNode.HideAllButAccessLevel,TargetNode.HideLocationsLevel) AS Hide
          FROM (
            SELECT 
              DISTINCT Anc.Ancestor AS NID
            FROM (
              SELECT L.NetworkNode AS NID FROM NodeLocation AS L 
        WHERE
              L.ActiveFlag = 1
          AND L.CascadedBBoxPt2Long >= ? AND L.CascadedBBoxPt1Long <= ?
          AND L.CascadedBBoxPt2Lat >= ? AND L.CascadedBBoxPt1Lat <= ?
   AND L.LongAngle >= ? UNION DISTINCT SELECT L.NetworkNode AS NID FROM NodeLocation AS L 
        WHERE
              L.ActiveFlag = 1
          AND L.CascadedBBoxPt2Long >= ? AND L.CascadedBBoxPt1Long <= ?
          AND L.CascadedBBoxPt2Lat >= ? AND L.CascadedBBoxPt1Lat <= ?
   AND L.LatAngle >= ?
            ) AS AncBase
            JOIN
              AncestorCollector AS Anc ON Anc.Node = AncBase.NID 
          ) AS TargetBase
          JOIN
            NetworkNode AS TargetNode ON TargetNode.Parent = TargetBase.NID AND TargetNode.ID != 11737939 AND TargetNode.Type IN (7273774, 7273777, 7273771)
          UNION DISTINCT
          SELECT
            7546063 AS NID,
            7273771 AS NodeType,
            NULL AS Parent,
            NULL AS Hide
        ) AS Node
        JOIN
          NodeName AS Nm ON Nm.NetworkNode = Node.NID AND Nm.Designation = 7273795
        JOIN
          NodeLocation AS HeirL ON HeirL.NetworkNode = Node.NID AND HeirL.ActiveFlag = 1
        LEFT JOIN
          ClimbingArea AS CA ON CA.NetworkNode = Node.NID
        LEFT JOIN
          URLStub AS Url ON Url.Node = Node.NID AND Url.Cannonised = 1
        LEFT JOIN
          TagAssignment AS TA ON TA.AssignedTo = Node.NID 
        LEFT JOIN
          Tag AS T ON T.ID = TA.AssignedTag AND T.TagType IN (SELECT ID FROM TagType WHERE TagType.ID = 198052585)
        GROUP BY
          Node.NID
  ) AS NodeStatBase
        LEFT JOIN
          RollupNodeStatistic AS NodeStat ON NodeStat.NetworkNode = NodeStatBase.NID
        LEFT JOIN
          DirectRouteStatistic AS RouteStat ON RouteStat.NetworkNode = NodeStatBase.NID
